<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/abf5b2fad2fa4f558685d7c738101d52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">首映场人数爆满，观影票也迅速售罄</p>
